== Results == The [[Democratic Labor Party]] won its only lower house seat at the 1973 election following the Liberal Party's incumbent for the northern Sydney seat of [[Electoral district of Gordon (New South Wales)|Gordon]] â [[Harry Jago]] failed to nominate in time. Conservative voters were urged to vote for the DLP candidate, [[Kevin Harrold]].
